          <En>A heavy block of metal, typically with a flat top, on which metal is placed to be shaped by hammering.</En>
          <Example>The blacksmith placed the hot iron on the anvil and began to hammer it into shape.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="f4bca953-a7fb-48da-a339-eb46eed74adb">
